<topic id="how_to_add_an_image_to_the_header">
    <title>How to Add an Image to the Header</title>
    <body>
        <p>The most common usecase is to add a background image to one of the page corners.</p>
        <codeblock outputclass="language-css">@page :left {
    @bottom-left-corner{
        <b>content</b>: " ";
        background-image: url('https://www.oxygenxml.com/resellers/resources/OxygenXMLEditor_icon.svg');
        background-repeat:no-repeat;
        background-position:50% 50%;        
    }
}</codeblock>
        <note type="important">Always specify a <keyword>content</keyword> property. If not, the page margin box will not be generated.</note>
        <note conref="dcpp_reusable_components.dita#reusable_components/note_pqy_hdn_vcb"/>
